## Research-first

- Search official docs (Next.js, Vercel, Google) before implementing
- Check for breaking changes (Next.js 15 differs from 14)
- Red flags: `pages/` patterns, `getStaticProps`/`getServerSideProps`, sitemap returning `loc` instead of `url`, missing `export default` on App Router pages

## SEO / GBP

- Localized title, meta description, H1 per page
- Sitemap: add new routes in `app/sitemap.ts` with priority and changeFrequency
- Schema: LocalBusiness on layout; WebPage/FAQPage etc. per page as needed
- Internal links: localized anchor text; image alt text includes location/service
